<h2>What is Patient Environment?</h2>
<p>Patient environment are the apps we use through which you can make appointments with our practice. You can also order repeat prescriptions, view your file, view laboratory results and do E-consults.</p>

<h2>Create an account</h2>
<p>If you don't have an account yet, please register:</p>
